  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nStar Atlas Recap 3-16-24\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video recapping recent Star Atlas news.\nStar Atlas GAO Insurance Debate\nOCG Thor posted a video on his thoughts about the GAO insurance debate in Star Atlas.\nMetaverse Nomads #138 Another $5m Ship Sold in Star Atlas?!\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video of their weekly Star Atlas livestream.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #121\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nSolana Weighs Significant Changes to Deal With Network Demand\nDecrypt published an article about Solana’s network demand issues.\nExclusive Interview – Star Atlas Titan Rainbow Phi Owner Reveal\nHologram News Network posted a video interview with the owner of a Star Atlas titan ship.\nThe Atlas Brew #103\nStar Atlas TV posted a video recording of the latest Atlas Brew.\nAtlas Brew #103: HRZ Continued – TLDR\nBeth posted a video recap of the latest Atlas Brew.",
